{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"b44975f126","title":"财政部关于分配城镇知识青年上山下乡工作业务费指标的通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"396e028368","index":0,"year":1976,"month":1,"day":7,"articleId":"b44975f126","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"b733063b68","name":"财政部"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2d2e62a8aa","type":"title","text":"财政部关于分配城镇知识青年上山下乡工作业务费指标的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b44975f126","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8f2e81a92e","type":"paragraph","text":"(75)财事字第329号","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b44975f126","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c62c9dd457","type":"paragraph","text":"省、市、自治区财政(财金)局、知青办公室：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b44975f126","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c62238dbf0","type":"paragraph","text":"为了进一步促进城镇知识青年上山下乡工作的开展，自一九七六年起，县以上知识青年上山下乡工作行政部门开展业务活动的经费，由国家预算安排“城镇知识青年上山下乡工作业务费(以下简称知青工作业务费)”。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b44975f126","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a7d53b2827","type":"paragraph","text":"现根据工作需要和本着“勤俭办一切事业”的原则，经与国务院知识青年上山下乡领导小组办公室研究，分配你省、市、自治区一九七六年知青工作业务费××万元。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b44975f126","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6511a743c7","type":"paragraph","text":"关于这项业务费的开支，作如下规定：","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b44975f126","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"158756bf03","type":"paragraph","text":"一、使用范围","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b44975f126","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5f8a419c5c","type":"paragraph","text":"1．会议费：指召开以知识青年为主的专业会议费。如，知识青年代表会、经验交流会、座谈会。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b44975f126","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d51fd55c72","type":"paragraph","text":"各级党委和革委会召开的知识青年工作会议，仍由行政经费开支。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b44975f126","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"9ff4f2dbb7","type":"paragraph","text":"2．宣传教育费：指对在乡知识青年进行宣传教育工作的开支。如，编印宣传材料和印刷知识青年登记表，举办小型先进事迹展览和报告会等费用。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b44975f126","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"603b5e64c4","type":"paragraph","text":"3．培训费：知识青年骨干、社队主管知青工作人员、带队干部的短期培训费。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b44975f126","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"69d1f141be","type":"paragraph","text":"二、知青工作业务费，不能用于办集体所有制青年队(场)和对动员下乡知识青年的困难补助。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b44975f126","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8dd73adc3c","type":"paragraph","text":"凡是在中发〔1973〕30号文件“附件一”第五条中规定，由安置经费开支的建房补助费、生活补助费、农家具补助费、学习材料费、医疗补助费、旅运费和用于下乡青年的特殊开支的其他费用，一律不准挪用知青工作业务费。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b44975f126","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4f572f093a","type":"paragraph","text":"下乡知识青年的业余教育、技术培训以及文体活动等费用，均由主办部门按其有关经费开支规定办理。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b44975f126","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"dae3732d06","type":"paragraph","text":"三、知青工作业务费，按一般事业费管理，年终结余不予结转。这项经费的使用，应本着勤俭节约的原则，精打细算，反对铺张浪费。","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b44975f126","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f26f6b60a6","type":"paragraph","text":"四、各省、市、自治区可以根据上述规定，结合实际情况，制定本地区的具体实施办法。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b44975f126","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3d821e6c3e","type":"paragraph","text":"(附表略)","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b44975f126","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f6e57b013a","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：根据文件的翻印件打印","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"b44975f126","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}